title: Mohammed Bakhati
text: Mohammed Farid Bakhati (date of birth and death unknowns) was an <a href="Egyptians">Egyptian</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> who played for <a href="Egypt%20national%20football%20team">Egypt</a> in the <a href="1934%20FIFA%20World%20Cup">1934 FIFA World Cup</a>. He also played for <a href="Zamalek%20SC">Zamalek SC</a>.
